    "description": "The photon simulator tries to import astropy, scipy, and xspec, and if any of these fail, they pass silently. This is to avoid irrelevant `ImportError`s when importing the whole `analysis_modules` API. \r\n\r\nI'm making them separate because the module will work without all of them, but when these imports were grouped together a failure to import any of them resulted in the following ones not being imported. \r\n\r\nWe probably ought to have some way of logging the failure to import, but only if one is trying to use the photon simulator module.",
    "created_on": "2014-02-17T02:29:38.910726+00:00",
